latestPosts.caption:
believe me, you’ll be fine wearing your clothes more than once 😌🫶🏻 and you’ll be fine without a cropped trench coat or a bubble skirt. since microtrends seem to be getting out of hand lately, i really think we should romanticize outfit repeating more - instead of constantly chasing new trends. because there’s nothing better than loving a fashion piece you can wear over and over again and always feel great in 🥰

First dump since forever 🌞🌵🍨 What was supposed to be 5 months of traveling East Asia turned into just 2 days in Mallorca. But that’s ok. Life doesn’t always go as planned and I try my best to take it as it comes - and to find happiness wherever l am 💛

And even though I was only there to shoot a collaboration, it reignited my love for island life in Europe. I could absolutely see myself living here for a while ☺️👀

And to anyone who might be going through a tough time right now: you’re not alone. Just know that whatever you’re feeling, others have been there too 🫂 And also one thing l’ve learned: even if you’re not in the mood, do what you usually enjoy. You can actually trick your body into feeling better - those happy hormones still show up, even if your mind’s not quite there yet 🥹
